-Drop the gun, you--
-[Hoonseok] Uh, e--excuse me.

619
00:38:33,791 --> 00:38:35,251
Sorry to interrupt.

620
00:38:35,335 --> 00:38:37,045
It's just that I've been listening
to you guys.

621
