Those gold bars, well, they're fake.

623
00:38:44,802 --> 00:38:47,764
[Hoonseok] Heeju asked me to make them,
so I did it for her.

624
00:38:47,847 --> 00:38:48,973
I was up all night.

625
00:38:50,183 --> 00:38:51,351
[Heeju] I was wondering.

626
00:38:52,018 --> 00:38:55,939
Could you make fake gold bars
that look exactly like these ones?

627
00:38:59,067 --> 00:39:00,193
Where are the real ones?

628
00:39:00,276 --> 00:39:02,320
Sorry, but I really don't know.

629
