I don't trust you, either.

634
00:39:13,915 --> 00:39:16,167
And obviously Heeju doesn't trust either
of us.

635
00:39:16,501 --> 00:39:18,211
At least it looks that way, right?

636
00:39:18,294 --> 00:39:20,463
That's why she wouldn't tell us where
the real gold bars are.

637
00:39:20,546 --> 00:39:22,006
[Woogy] Ah, shit.

638
00:39:22,757 --> 00:39:24,092
And you know what she told me?

639
00:39:24,509 --> 00:39:26,427
She said if she lost the gold bars...

640
00:39:27,011 --> 00:39:28,972
...she wouldn't even want to live anymore.

641
00:39:29,722 --> 00:39:31,474
[Woogy] That if it came to that...

642
00:39:32,517 --> 00:39:34,268
...then I should just let her die.

643
