until you talk.
And you will talk.

667
00:41:29,634 --> 00:41:31,052
Promise you that.

668
00:41:33,096 --> 00:41:34,764
I really mean it.

669
00:41:35,890 --> 00:41:37,100
I don't know.

670
00:41:38,559 --> 00:41:40,269
[Chairman Ahn] Mr. Jin.

671
