What if I let Kim Heeju go
and you made off with the gold bars?

694
00:42:45,626 --> 00:42:47,211
[Jinman] Meet me at the Gold Resort.

695
00:42:47,295 --> 00:42:48,504
6:00 o'clock.

696
00:42:48,963 --> 00:42:50,339
I'll bring the gold bars there.

697
00:42:51,382 --> 00:42:52,592
You can check them then.

698
00:42:54,010 --> 00:42:55,303
And release Kim Heeju.

699
