[Chairman Ahn] This whole situation
just doesn't add up.

700
00:43:00,474 --> 00:43:02,685
The gold bars are in your hands right now.

701
00:43:05,104 --> 00:43:06,898
And you're saying you'd give them up
for this girl?

702
