What's going on here, Detective?

703
00:43:08,524 --> 00:43:09,609
[clicks tongue]

704
00:43:10,359 --> 00:43:12,486
Kim Heeju is my daughter.

705
00:43:13,821 --> 00:43:15,114
[Jinman] Does it all make sense
to you now?

706
00:43:17,867 --> 00:43:19,702
[Chairman Ahn] Oh, wow!

707
00:43:19,785 --> 00:43:21,162
[laughing]

708
00:43:21,245 --> 00:43:22,580
Is that right?

709
00:43:22,663 --> 00:43:23,915
[laughs]

710
00:43:23,998 --> 00:43:25,249
You know what?

711
00:43:25,333 --> 00:43:27,084
Yeah, that does make sense now.

712
00:43:27,168 --> 00:43:29,045
-[laughs]
-[Jinman] Let me talk to her for a minute.

713
00:43:29,128 --> 00:43:30,421
