714
00:43:31,130 --> 00:43:32,715
Oh, no.

715
00:43:32,798 --> 00:43:35,009
What would you do if I killed her already?

716
00:43:35,843 --> 00:43:37,053
Well then I guess...

717
00:43:38,012 --> 00:43:39,597
