[Heeju breathing erratically]

720
00:43:50,316 --> 00:43:51,484
-[Chairman Ahn] Hey.
-[coughing]

721
00:43:52,693 --> 00:43:55,696
Kim Jinman.
He says he's your father.

722
00:43:55,780 --> 00:43:58,783
[shallow breathing]

723
00:44:02,703 --> 00:44:05,706
[Heeju breathing]

724
00:44:06,123 --> 00:44:07,583
[Heeju] Hey.

725
00:44:08,751 --> 00:44:09,752
Hey.

726
00:44:10,586 --> 00:44:11,921
Keep hanging in there.

727
00:44:12,004 --> 00:44:13,547
I'll save you.

728
00:44:13,631 --> 00:44:15,174
[exhales]

729
00:44:16,008 --> 00:44:19,011
[shallow breathing]
STYLE
::cue()

