731
00:44:41,367 --> 00:44:44,370
[glass shatters]

732
00:45:11,981 --> 00:45:14,984
[engine rumbling]

733
00:45:18,154 --> 00:45:21,157
[birds chirping]

734
00:45:31,083 --> 00:45:32,251
[Jinman] Hey.

735
00:45:33,419 --> 00:45:34,628
Give this to Kim Heeju.

736
00:45:35,629 --> 00:45:37,173
[Woogy] What is it?

737
00:45:37,923 --> 00:45:39,550
Just give it to her.
She'll know.

738
