Why don't you give it to her yourself?

739
00:45:42,636 --> 00:45:44,889
Do as I say, little shit.

740
00:45:46,891 --> 00:45:48,017
[Woogy] Detective, wait.

741
00:45:50,019 --> 00:45:51,020
You up for a smoke?

742
00:45:52,146 --> 00:45:53,272
[car door opens]

743
00:45:54,523 --> 00:45:55,983
[exhales]

744
00:45:57,193 --> 00:45:58,194
Detective.

745
00:46:01,405 --> 00:46:02,448
Are you scared?

746
00:46:08,120 --> 00:46:10,664
[inhales on cigarette]

747
00:46:13,209 --> 00:46:14,919
I'm fuckin' scared to death right now.

748
00:46:15,586 --> 00:46:17,046
How 'bout you?

749
00:46:17,671 --> 00:46:19,340
[chuckles]

750
00:46:23,386 --> 00:46:24,595
Yeah, me, too.

751
00:46:24,678 --> 00:46:25,971
[Jinman inhales on cigarette]

752
00:46:26,514 --> 00:46:28,099
[Woogy inhales]

753
00:46:28,182 --> 00:46:29,850
This chitchat is useless.

754
00:46:30,393 --> 00:46:32,019
Look, if you hear a gunshot...

755
00:46:33,562 --> 00:46:35,523
...don't fuck around.
Just come right away.

756
00:46:38,067 --> 00:46:39,568
Hey, Detective.

757
00:46:40,736 --> 00:46:43,781
When I see Heeju,
I'll tell her you got out safely.

758
00:46:45,199 --> 00:46:47,034
What the hell are you talking about?

759
00:46:47,368 --> 00:46:48,411
I'll survive.

760
00:46:49,412 --> 00:46:50,496
[car door opens]

761
00:46:52,331 --> 00:46:56,585
[car door closes]

762
00:46:56,669 --> 00:47:00,589
[engines revving]

763
00:47:00,673 --> 00:47:03,259
[♪ melancholy music]

764
00:47:27,199 --> 00:47:30,202
[♪ tense music]

765
00:47:44,300 --> 00:47:45,301
[car door opens]
[Jinman coughs]

766
00:48:03,194 --> 00:48:04,278
[sniffs]

767
00:48:05,988 --> 00:48:07,072
Go look.

768
00:48:07,156 --> 00:48:08,491
[Jo] Yes, sir.

769
00:48:23,839 --> 00:48:25,382
[Mr. Jang] Let's see.

770
00:48:29,845 --> 00:48:31,096
[Mr. Jang] Oh, shit!

771
00:48:31,180 --> 00:48:33,015
[laughs]

772
00:48:35,768 --> 00:48:37,561
[exhales]

773
00:48:47,613 --> 00:48:48,614
[gold clinks]
STYLE
::cue()

774
00:48:50,824 --> 00:48:52,159
Looks good, Chairman Ahn!

775
00:48:55,204 --> 00:48:56,455
Send Kim Heeju over!

776
00:48:59,208 --> 00:49:00,209
Okay.

777
00:49:01,502 --> 00:49:04,505
[breathing erratically]

778
00:49:18,435 --> 00:49:19,687
